<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="recognition-n">recognition <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌrekəɡ'nɪʃn/    美 /ˌrekəɡ'nɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>认出；识别；承认：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The town has <strong>changed beyond all recognition</strong> since I was last here. 
自从我上次离开这里，这座小城已变得让人认不出来了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is general <strong>recognition that</strong> the study techniques of many students are weak.
人们普遍意识到很多学生的学习技能薄弱。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>face / speech recognition
面部 / 语音识别</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I haven’t seen Sara since she was a little girl, and she has changed beyond <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (recognize).  （2010 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. recognition  </p></div>